      <title>三星支持学术人工智能机器人为学生和学者提供服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/samsung-backs-scholarly-ai-bot-serving-students-and-academics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Liner 是一家为学生和研究人员打造的人工智能搜索引擎，该公司已从 Intervest、Atinum Investment 和 Samsung Venture 等投资者处筹集了 2900 万美元，以拓展其在专业信息检索领域的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/samsung-backs-scholarly-ai-bot-serving-students-and-academics</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
