    <item>
      <title>亚洲 IT 领军企业 TCS 业绩落后于预期，表明科技支出疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/asia-it-leader-tcs-lags-estimates-in-sign-of-weak-tech-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔塔咨询服务有限公司的季度利润低于分析师的预期，这表明从银行到零售商等客户仍然不愿意在信息技术上进行大规模投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/asia-it-leader-tcs-lags-estimates-in-sign-of-weak-tech-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:47:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
